{
  "id": "adv_event_2204_01_02",
  "title": "愛歌う星の継承者 2話 聴けば聴くほど",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei001.wav",
      "text": "う～ん、レッスンの後のご飯は美味しいな～",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio001.wav",
      "text": "分からないわ",
      "startTime": 8.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz001.wav",
      "text": "何が分からないんですの？",
      "startTime": 10.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今回の企画、どうして琴乃やさくらじゃなくて",
      "startTime": 12.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio002.wav",
      "text": "すずが選ばれたのか、よ",
      "startTime": 16.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn001.wav",
      "text": "私……ですか？",
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "普通に考えるなら、妹の琴乃なり",
      "startTime": 22.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio003.wav",
      "text": "麻奈と縁の深いさくらが選ばれるのが妥当でしょ？",
      "startTime": 25.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio004.wav",
      "text": "その方が、テレビ的には話題性があるわ",
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "芽衣はすずにゃんが猫っぽくて可愛いからかな",
      "startTime": 32.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei002.wav",
      "text": "って思ってたよ",
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そ、そう思うのは芽衣だけですわ……",
      "startTime": 38.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz002.wav",
      "text": "私が星見プロで一番歌がうまいからに決まっています！",
      "startTime": 42.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すずはまだまだこれからでしょう",
      "startTime": 47.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio005.wav",
      "text": "今この時点での歌唱力だけなら、もっと上はいるわ",
      "startTime": 50.71,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn002.wav",
      "text": "り、莉央さん？　すずだって、歌は上手で――",
      "startTime": 54.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei003.wav",
      "text": "確かに！　芽衣、瑠依ちゃんの歌聴きたいかも！",
      "startTime": 58.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn003.wav",
      "text": "ちょっ、ちょっと芽衣まで",
      "startTime": 63.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz003.wav",
      "text": "あああなた達！　私に喧嘩を売っているんですわね！？",
      "startTime": 66.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そこまでおっしゃるのなら",
      "startTime": 71.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz004.wav",
      "text": "今回の仕事を立派にやり遂げて、証明してみせますわ！",
      "startTime": 73.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私が、一番、麻奈様の曲を歌いこなせるということを！",
      "startTime": 78.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz005.wav",
      "text": "次の伝説は、私、成宮すずがつくるということを！",
      "startTime": 84.2766666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "随分と大きく出たわね",
      "startTime": 90.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio006.wav",
      "text": "口だけにならないといいけど",
      "startTime": 93.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "成宮家の人間たるもの、言った言葉に責任は持ちますわ",
      "startTime": 95.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz006.wav",
      "text": "今から特訓します！　芽衣、付き合って下さいまし！",
      "startTime": 100.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいよ～、これ食べ終わったら――って",
      "startTime": 105.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei004.wav",
      "text": "芽衣はまだ食べてるよーっ！　引っ張らないで～",
      "startTime": 109.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio007.wav",
      "text": "ふふっ、これであの子のステージが楽しみになったわ",
      "startTime": 116.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn004.wav",
      "text": "え？　莉央さん、それはどういう……",
      "startTime": 121.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あの子は暴走するくらい張り切った方が",
      "startTime": 125.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio008.wav",
      "text": "実力以上のパフォーマンスを出すものね……",
      "startTime": 128.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もしかして、わざとですか？",
      "startTime": 131.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn005.wav",
      "text": "すずのこと、よく見てるんですね",
      "startTime": 135.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かりやすい子だもの",
      "startTime": 138.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio009.wav",
      "text": "ふふっ、すずには内緒よ",
      "startTime": 140.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 143.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まずは、お手本となる麻奈様の『Precious』を",
      "startTime": 144.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz007.wav",
      "text": "このライブ映像で徹底的に研究するのですわ！",
      "startTime": 148.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 152.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei005.wav",
      "text": "だね！　いっぱい聴いて完コピしようよ！",
      "startTime": 152.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 157.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふふ……もうすでに何千回も聴いているのですが",
      "startTime": 157.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz008.wav",
      "text": "さらに上を目指しますわ",
      "startTime": 162.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 164.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央さんを驚かせてみせますわ！",
      "startTime": 164.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz009.wav",
      "text": "では、麻奈様のライブを再生しますわよ！",
      "startTime": 167.8433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02(tokyosuzroom-00-noon)",
      "startTime": 171.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
